description:
Find your flow with the Cork Yoga Mat - Natural Balance by Yoga Design Lab. Designed for stability and sustainability, this eco-friendly mat blends premium cork with a natural rubber base for superior grip, durability, and comfort. The minimalist geometric design inspires alignment and mindfulness, while the moisture-activated surface ensures non-slip support through every pose. Ideal for all practices, from grounding yin sessions to dynamic vinyasa flows. Elevate your practice with nature‚ is finest.


Sustainably harvested cork for a non-slip surface that gets grippier with moisture

Naturally antimicrobial to resist odors and bacteria, keeping your mat fresh

Free from PVC and toxic chemicals for a safe and eco-friendly practice

Lightweight and durable for easy transport and long-lasting performance

Biodegradable materials to reduce your environmental footprint

Carry Strap Included: Comes with a durable strap for easy transport to and from your practice.


Move with balance. Move with nature. üåø




  const observer = new MutationObserver(function (mutations) {
    mutations.forEach(function (mutation) {
      mutation.addedNodes.forEach(function (node) {
        if (node.nodeType === 1) { // ensure it's an element
          // Check if it's the image or contains the image
          const targetImg = node.matches?.('img[alt="icon"]') 
            ? node 
            : node.querySelector?.('img[alt="icon"]');

          if (targetImg) {
            targetImg.setAttribute("alt", "recycled water bottle counter");
          }
        }
      });
    });
  });

  observer.observe(document.body, {
    childList: true,
    subtree: true
  });

Take your practice anywhere with the Travel Combo Yoga Mat - Zenith, a lightweight, foldable, and ultra-versatile mat designed for yogis on the go. Featuring a stunning blend of celestial hues and geometric symmetry, this mat brings inspiration and balance to every movement.
With a moisture-activated microfiber surface fused to natural rubber, it delivers exceptional grip as you sweat, making it ideal for hot yoga, vinyasa, and travel-friendly flows.


Compact and portable: Folds like a towel for effortless transport.

All-in-One Design: Say goodbye to slippery layers‚ this mat fuses a natural rubber base with a moisture-activated microfiber surface for unmatched grip and convenience.

Eco-Friendly Materials: Made with a natural rubber base and recycled PET microfiber, printed using water-based inks. Free of silicone, toxic glue, and phthalates, it‚ is a conscious choice for you and the planet.

Moisture-Activated Grip: The surface becomes grippier as you sweat, supporting your transitions and deeper poses with ease.

Perfect For All Styles: Ideal for hot yoga, vinyasa, power yoga, restorative sessions, and more, providing the support and grip needed for every flow.

Carry Strap Included: Comes with a durable strap for easy transport to and from your practice.

Stay grounded wherever you go with Zenith - designed for movement, made for adventure.



